Package ClusterCore

Core classes for cluster analysis

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FuzzyCMeans
    Fuzzy-C-Means (FCM) Cluster analysis with Fuzzy-C-Means clustering algorithm Step 1: Initialization Step 2: Determination of the cluster centers Step 3: Calculate the new partition matrix Step 4: Termination or repetition Step 5: optional - Repeat calculation (steps 2 to 4)
    Point2D
    Point with 2D coordinates
    PointPixel
    Point with pixel coordinates
    PossibilisticCMeans
    Possivilistic-C-Means (PCM) Cluster analysis with Possivilistic-C-Means clustering algorithm Step 1: Initialization Step 2: Determination of the cluster centers Step 3: Calculate the new partition matrix and ni Step 4: Termination or repetition Step 5: optional - Repeat calculation (steps 2 to 4)
